(As the story begins, the master falls ill. The Shirabyōshi, 
determined to uphold her master's art, heads to the mountains 
for training and meets the enigmatic twin butterflies.)

(A disciple of a master sword dancer, yet disregarding their 
footsteps, this performer earns a living with unusual acts 
using an <i>Ōdachi</i> passed down to them.)
